    Engine
    Engine.tickAuto(Scheduler scheduler)
    Allows the engine to manage idle timeout processing by providing it the single threaded executor context where all transport work is done which ensures singled threaded access while removing the need for the client library or server application to manage calls to the Engine.tick(long) methods.
